1
00:00:03,461 --> 00:00:04,754
Me.

2
00:00:08,341 --> 00:00:10,552
I think I might really start to like you a lot.

3
00:00:15,849 --> 00:00:17,267
Maybe I already do.

4
00:00:24,524 --> 00:00:27,944
Can I stay over?

5
00:01:48,441 --> 00:01:49,984
So what?

6
00:01:56,241 --> 00:01:57,033
Ah!

7
00:02:01,871 --> 00:02:03,289
You spilled it last time too.

8
00:02:04,749 --> 00:02:06,292
I did it on purpose to flirt.

9
00:02:07,043 --> 00:02:08,503
But this time, it’s for real.

10
00:02:11,131 --> 00:02:14,384
Didn’t you know I did it on purpose? You're so naïve...

11
00:02:15,969 --> 00:02:19,472
Or maybe I pretended to fall for it. Who's naïve now...

12
00:02:20,348 --> 00:02:23,434
You talk like a real college professor, huh?

13
00:02:24,561 --> 00:02:26,312
I’ll take you home later.

14
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,693
Don’t you have work tomorrow?

15
00:02:32,527 --> 00:02:34,028
Where do you work?

16
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:39,325
Ah~ yeah, gotta go to work.

17
00:02:51,796 --> 00:02:53,298
- Time to tell the truth.

18
00:02:54,757 --> 00:02:56,301
- I'm not a 32-year-old office worker.

19
00:02:57,218 --> 00:02:59,387
- I’m a 22-year-old college student.

20
00:03:19,115 --> 00:03:19,949
Hello?

21
00:03:20,742 --> 00:03:23,077
- Let’s meet at that bar.

22
00:03:24,287 --> 00:03:25,496
Maybe not there...

23
00:03:25,496 --> 00:03:26,956
- I'm already out front.

24
00:03:27,999 --> 00:03:28,958
- Take your time.

25
00:03:45,225 --> 00:03:46,976
Oh? You're back again?

26
00:03:47,101 --> 00:03:47,685
Yeah.

27
00:03:48,645 --> 00:03:50,313
With Howon?

28
00:03:50,855 --> 00:03:53,650
Ah… yeah, I guess?

29
00:03:57,153 --> 00:03:57,946
I lost.

30
00:03:59,948 --> 00:04:00,740
Huh?

31
00:04:02,492 --> 00:04:05,286
Ah~ no, it’s nothing.

32
00:04:06,955 --> 00:04:11,084
By the way, are you here looking for Howon?

33
00:04:12,001 --> 00:04:14,295
Well, not exactly "looking for" him...

34
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:17,257
Look, I can’t give you Howon’s number.

35
00:04:17,715 --> 00:04:19,467
I gave it out a few times before,

36
00:04:19,467 --> 00:04:21,302
and things got messy, more than once.

37
00:04:22,053 --> 00:04:24,180
So now I never give it out.

38
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:27,183
Don't get your hopes up and just go.

39
00:04:28,768 --> 00:04:31,396
You think Howon and I haven’t met since that day?

40
00:04:31,396 --> 00:04:33,815
And that I don’t even have his number?

41
00:04:34,190 --> 00:04:35,525
Of course not.

42
00:04:36,150 --> 00:04:39,946
Anyway, he's not here, so please just go.

43
00:04:42,073 --> 00:04:43,366
Uh...

44
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:46,828
Why are you so sure Howon isn’t seeing me?

45
00:04:46,828 --> 00:04:47,662
Huh?

46
00:04:48,246 --> 00:04:51,332
Because I made a bet on it, that's why.

47
00:04:58,673 --> 00:04:59,966
Howon.

48
00:05:09,767 --> 00:05:11,311
So you bet on me, huh?

49
00:05:13,563 --> 00:05:14,897
Guess you won?

50
00:05:18,818 --> 00:05:20,236
That’s why I asked you not to..

51
00:05:21,696 --> 00:05:23,740
If it was just fun for you, then please leave.

52
00:05:26,409 --> 00:05:28,119
Why make such a big deal out of a one-night bet?

53
00:05:28,786 --> 00:05:30,621
One night isn’t enough for me.

54
00:05:31,122 --> 00:05:32,999
You’re totally my type.

55
00:05:36,169 --> 00:05:40,173
- That’s not what I really wanted to say...

56
00:05:42,383 --> 00:05:43,968
That’s all I meant to you, right?

57
00:05:44,802 --> 00:05:45,511
Yeah.

58
00:05:46,179 --> 00:05:49,682
Did you really think I was gonna get serious with you?

59
00:05:53,353 --> 00:05:55,396
- Once you start lying from the heart,

60
00:05:56,105 --> 00:05:57,774
- it's hard to stop.

61
00:05:58,191 --> 00:06:00,109
We were good together in bed.

62
00:06:00,902 --> 00:06:04,113
That's rare. It’d be a waste for just once.

63
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,785
Just be honest with me.

64
00:06:09,952 --> 00:06:11,454
Tell me what was a lie,

65
00:06:12,747 --> 00:06:14,207
and what was real.

66
00:06:16,542 --> 00:06:20,088
I’ll listen... and forgive you.

67
00:06:22,340 --> 00:06:25,968
- You should forget a piece of trash like me quickly.

68
00:06:28,638 --> 00:06:30,598
Take care. It was fun.

69
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:33,851
Lee Howon!

70
00:06:35,770 --> 00:06:36,938
I'm not done talking!

71
00:06:38,314 --> 00:06:39,607
Well, I am.

72
00:06:40,358 --> 00:06:42,110
Stop being so pathetic.

73
00:06:42,610 --> 00:06:44,153
I really hate that
